title: Repaint! Pastel Kitty collaboration with Doll Motion
author: Dollightful
description:
Done in collaboration with fellow cat enthusiast Doll Motion, I put together a tiny pastel kitty cat doll in the spirit of spring. 


See @DollMotion ‘s cat doll here! 
https://youtu.be/UffSpgI_udQ
--------------------------------------------
Merchandise:
https://www.zazzle.com/store/dollightful/collections
https://society6.com/dollightful
Doll clothing patterns here: https://www.etsy.com/shop/DollightfulPatterns
Instagram, Twitter, Pinterest: @dollightfully
--------------------------------------------
MATERIALS
Hujoo “Nano Freya” from http://junkyspot.com/
Yarn - %100 Acrylic
Fabric – cotton
Ribbon – 3/8 inch/9.5 mm 
Paints – Acrylic (Liquitex)
Paints – Gouache (Caran D’ache)
Water Color Pencils (Faber Castell)
Mr. Super Clear UV Flat (wear a mask and spray in a ventilated area!)
MASK: Organic Vapor Particle Respirator Mask
Varnish (DuraClear)
Resin – 2-Part Jewel Resin (www.clayndeco.com)
Gram Scale
Resin Eye Molds (Padico) I used the 12mm size hemisphere.
Paint for eye whites – Game Air “Dead White” (Vallejo)
Glue (205 OKONG 오공본드)
--------------------------------------------
Musical tracks from Artlist https://artlist.io 
Brand New Toy – Ty Simon
Baby Smile – Lux-Inspira
Squeaky Clean – Josh Leake
Grin and Skip – Bamtone
Summer Snow (Instrumental) – Low Light
Shimmer – Wolf Samuels
Take me to the Beach – Raz Burg
Cheerful - Bamtone
--------------------------------------------
Logo and other graphics designed by: https://charliesparksdesign.myportfolio.com/
--------------------------------------------

localize.description:
我与猫咪爱好者Doll Motion合作，在春天的精神下制作了一个小小的粉色猫咪公仔。


点击这里查看@DollMotion 的猫咪公仔。
https://youtu.be/UffSpgI_udQ
--------------------------------------------
商品。
https://www.zazzle.com/store/dollightful/collections
https://society6.com/dollightful
娃娃服装图案这里：https://www.etsy.com/shop/DollightfulPatterns
Instagram, Twitter, Pinterest: @dollightfully
--------------------------------------------
材料
Hujoo "Nano Freya" from http://junkyspot.com/
纱线 - %100丙烯酸
布料 - 棉
色带--3/8英寸/9.5毫米。
油漆-丙烯酸（Liquitex）
油漆--水粉(Caran D ache)
水彩铅笔(Faber Castell)
超清UV平先生（戴上口罩，在通风的地方喷！）。
MASK: 有机蒸汽粒子呼吸器口罩
清漆(DuraClear)
树脂 - 2-部分宝石树脂 (www.clayndeco.com)
克级
树脂眼模（Padico）我用的是12mm大小的半球。
眼白的油漆--游戏空气 "死白"（Vallejo）。
胶水 (205 OKONG 오공본드)
--------------------------------------------
